WEBVTT

00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:30.059
In pandemics, robust, agile supply chains

00:08:30.083 --> 00:08:32.893
deliver the masks, ventilators,

00:08:32.917 --> 00:08:35.476
testing kits and vaccines

00:08:35.500 --> 00:08:37.059
that we all need.

00:08:37.083 --> 00:08:38.851
It saves lives,

00:08:38.875 --> 00:08:41.750
and it helps to reopen our economy.

00:08:42.333 --> 00:08:45.851
Suppliers don't just matter
when we're in a crisis.

00:08:45.875 --> 00:08:48.559
If you really want to scale
your positive impact,

00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:51.476
you have to look beyond
the walls of your company.

00:08:51.500 --> 00:08:52.809
BHP Billiton,

00:08:52.833 --> 00:08:54.559
the Australian mining company,

00:08:54.583 --> 00:08:56.768
did just that when it made a commitment

00:08:56.792 --> 00:09:01.143
to end gender imbalance
in its workforce by 2025.